snippet.title: The Incredibles: Jack-Jack’s Escape
snippet.description: Heroic Baby Hijinx! The game takes place within the Underminer’s colossal digger. You control Jack-Jack , the infant member of the Incredibles. Guide Jack-Jack as he single-handedly and unknowingly destroys the monstrous machine within as his family fights the villain on the surface.
